        <div class="commentnew" id="comment-1125404">


	<div class="commentheader"><div class="report" style="float:right;"><a href="http://www.boingboing.net/2011/05/30/mexico-kindergarten.html#comment-1125404">#11</a> <span class="separator">&bull;</span>  2:07 AM, May 31
		
		
